It stresses the importance of verifying the presence of bats before maintaining the properties, because by destroying without the desire of a single maternity nest, the death of 400 female and small, or even the disappearance of an entire local population, can be caused.
The bats are protected and it is illegal to kill them, to disturb them, or to destroy their paths.
